---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Perimeter Security">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="relative h-[300px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://www.fen-bayservices.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/shutterstock_1342427225.jpg" 
        alt="Perimeter Security" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Perimeter Security</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Advanced Unauthorized Access Detection</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Our system uses advanced artificial intelligence to monitor worker and vehicle movement in industrial environments. The system automatically detects unauthorized access and potentially dangerous situations, enabling immediate response from security personnel.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <img 
          src="https://protex-image-asset-cdn.s3.eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/Housekeeping/Worker+distance+to+vehicle.+(housekeeping)+gif.gif"
          alt="Worker Detection"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div>
        <img 
          src="https://grekkom.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/grekkom-perimeter-lookout-ai.jpg"
          alt="Factory Security"
          class="rounded-lg shadow-lg w-full"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="prose lg:prose-xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Comprehensive Facility Protection</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          The system provides continuous monitoring of the facility perimeter, identifying and classifying all activities. Integration with existing security systems enables quick response to potential threats and maintains a high level of security.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose lg:prose-xl mt-8">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>24/7 automated monitoring</li>
        <li>Advanced motion detection</li>
        <li>Object and threat classification</li>
        <li>Instant alert system</li>
        <li>Integration with existing security systems</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="my-8">
        <h2>See It In Action</h2>
        <div class="aspect-w-16 aspect-h-9">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jOARPYVntEU"
            title="Product Demo"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            class="w-full h-[400px]"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>